snippet.title: Goat MMO Simulator - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Goat MMO Simulator is a free expansion for Goat Simulator. It will automatically be patched into the game for everyone who owns Goat Simulator on Steam.

We're on Facebook too: https://www.facebook.com/GoatSimulator

Also twitter: https://twitter.com/Coffee_Stain
